<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=8647&amp;p=90342#p90342"><![CDATA[
You're reading from mapped video memory in one place, then using the VRAM array in another place.<br /><br />What goes into the "byte buffer" should be what's in mapped video memory, not simply the contents of "VRAM".<br /><br />Edit: Re-read your second post.  The delay happens with reading character data as well, why are you immediately returning the value?  I didn't see that part where there was a return in the middle of the IF block.<br /><br /><br />Edit: I think this should do it:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">uint8_t readPPU&#40;uint16_t addr&#41; &#123;<br />   uint8_t tempbyte;<br />   addr &amp;= 0x3FFF;<br />   if &#40;addr&gt;=0x3F00&#41; addr = 0x3F00 | &#40;addr &amp; 0x1F&#41;;<br />   if &#40;addr&gt;0x2FFF &amp;&amp; addr&lt;0x3F00&#41; addr = 0x3000 | &#40;addr &amp; 0xEFF&#41;;<br />   if &#40;addr&gt;=0x2000 &amp;&amp; addr&lt;0x2400&#41; addr = &#40;addr - 0x2000&#41; + PPU-&gt;ntmap&#91;0&#93;;<br />      else if &#40;addr&gt;=0x2400 &amp;&amp; addr&lt;0x2800&#41; addr = &#40;addr - 0x2400&#41; + PPU-&gt;ntmap&#91;1&#93;;<br />      else if &#40;addr&gt;=0x2800 &amp;&amp; addr&lt;0x2C00&#41; addr = &#40;addr - 0x2800&#41; + PPU-&gt;ntmap&#91;2&#93;;<br />      else if &#40;addr&gt;=0x2C00 &amp;&amp; addr&lt;0x3000&#41; addr = &#40;addr - 0x2C00&#41; + PPU-&gt;ntmap&#91;3&#93;;<br />   if &#40;addr&lt;0x2000&#41; &#123;<br />      tempbyte = cartridge.CHRbank&#91;addr&gt;&gt;10&#93;&#91;addr&amp;1023&#93;;<br />      if &#40;cartridge.mapper == 9&#41; &#123;<br />         switch &#40;addr &amp; 0x3FF0&#41; &#123;<br />            case 0x0FD0: map9-&gt;latch1 = 0xFD; CHRswap&#40;&amp;cartridge, 0, map9-&gt;latch0_fd, 4096&#41;; break;<br />            case 0x0FE0: map9-&gt;latch1 = 0xFE; CHRswap&#40;&amp;cartridge, 0, map9-&gt;latch0_fe, 4096&#41;; break;<br />            case 0x1FD0: map9-&gt;latch2 = 0xFD; CHRswap&#40;&amp;cartridge, 1, map9-&gt;latch1_fd, 4096&#41;; break;<br />            case 0x1FE0: map9-&gt;latch2 = 0xFE; CHRswap&#40;&amp;cartridge, 1, map9-&gt;latch1_fe, 4096&#41;; break;<br />         &#125;<br />      &#125;<br /><br />//new code:<br />uint8_t oldbyte = PPU-&gt;bytebuffer;<br />PPU-&gt;bytebuffer = tempbyte;<br />return oldbyte;<br />   &#125;<br />   if &#40;addr &gt;= 0x3F00&#41; tempbyte = VRAM&#91;addr&#93;;<br />      else tempbyte = PPU-&gt;bytebuffer;<br />   PPU-&gt;bytebuffer = VRAM&#91;addr&#93;;<br />   return&#40;tempbyte&#41;;<br />&#125;<br /></div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Wed Feb 22, 2012 3:04 pm</p><hr />
